    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? This car is an absolute gem! It's been pampered since day one\u2014spotless interior, gleaming paint, and it runs like a total dream. Honestly, you won't find one in better shape; it\u2019s basically perfect. It is the ideal treat for someone who wants that new-car magic. Come take a look and fall in love!",
