    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit is mechanically flawless, with a recently serviced VANOS system and documented rod bearing replacement for preventative maintenance. The chassis remains rigid with a verified rear subframe reinforcement kit already installed. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory variable M differential lock. The suspension maintains its original geometry with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, ensuring the legendary handling characteristics are preserved. The exterior features original Laguna Seca Blue paint with consistent depth readings across all panels, housing staggered OEM Style 67 forged wheels. A true turn-key enthusiast vehicle with zero fluid leaks or vacuum issues.",
